title: Arsenal Legends - Martin Keown
description:
An unsung hero to many, the rugged defender became an Arsenal great through his will to win and uncompromising style of play on the pitch. As intelligent as he is tenacious, few have left a legacy at Arsenal like that of Martin Keown.

Through two spells and over 400 games for Arsenal, Martin Keown made himself a legend at the club through his rugged style and peerless determination. From a youth team player in the early 80s to a senior figure in the 'Invincibles' of 03/04, Keown is a part of the fabric of Arsenal and his influence is still felt today, in the stands and in the trophy cabinet.

Quality: 720p
